name: space guardian Gum
description:
"In a place far beyond the stars someone takes care to keep the peace there where it all begins, preventing the power stored in that place from falling into the hands of crazy aliens and creatures never imagined. Gum protects th First Star and the First People at all costs but without losing the sweetness."

this work was created in the pixelpetz game by me (@eitaivan). i produced a series of original alien characters, exploring linking science fiction, fantasy and horror references.
